{
  "texts": [
    "The participants were also given the opportunity to seek clarification or pose questions related to the study as suggested by (Gill et al., 2008).",
    "These interviews were conducted individually, either in person or through online meetings, in September 2023.",
    "All collected data were anonymised to safeguard participant privacy.",
    "Table 1 presents a snapshot of the respondents' demographic profiles, indicating a cohort of thirty-nine males and thirty-six female's participants, primarily aged > 25 years.",
    "The participants were mixed of undergraduate, Masters and PhD academicians with more than two years of academic and research experience."
  ]
}